FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775927152
OL,3,CNI political leader write to Starmer
OL,4,Crequesting action against fuel costs
OL,6,FThey have asked the Government to look
OL,7,Fat reducing fuel duty, targeted
OL,8,Fsupport for hauliers, farmers and
OL,9,Fsmall and medium enterprises, and a
OL,10,Fcomprehensive cost-of-living support
OL,11,Fpackage.
OL,13,FIn a joint statement, Ms O'Neill and
OL,14,FMs Little-Pengelly said they were
OL,15,F"deeply concerned about the escalating
OL,16,Fpressures facing families, workers and
OL,17,Fbusinesses as fuel and energy costs
OL,18,Fcontinue to rise".
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
