CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775927152
OL,3,CNI political leader write to Starmer
OL,4,Crequesting action against fuel costs
OL,6,FThey added: "The cost of fuel is
OL,7,Fputting significant pressure on, with
OL,8,Fincreases not sustainable.
OL,10,F"These pressures are being felt in
OL,11,Ffamily homes here and beyond.
OL,13,F"Alongside rising fuel costs and
OL,14,Fescalating energy bills, there is also
OL,15,Fan impact on businesses.
OL,26,@nD@MOUrD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775927152
OL,3,CNI political leader write to Starmer
OL,4,Crequesting action against fuel costs
OL,6,F"Our hauliers, our farmers and small
OL,7,Fand medium-sized enterprises are
OL,8,Ffacing sharply increased operating
OL,9,Fcosts too, and these costs are
OL,10,Finevitably being passed on further,
OL,11,Fdeepening the cost-of-living crisis.
OL,13,F"Families and businesses cannot
OL,14,Fcontinue to absorb these sustained
OL,15,Fincreases without intervention, which
OL,16,Fis why we are calling on the Prime
OL,17,FMinister to bring forward a package of
OL,18,Fmeasures to support those under
OL,19,Fpressure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775927152
OL,3,CNI political leader write to Starmer
OL,4,Crequesting action against fuel costs
OL,6,F"This package should include a
OL,7,Freduction in fuel duty to ease
OL,8,Fpressure on both households and
OL,9,Fbusinesses, targeted support for
OL,10,Fhauliers, farmers and SMEs, and a
OL,11,Fcomprehensive cost-of-living support
OL,12,Fpackage."
OL,14,FMs O'Neill and Ms Little-Pengelly
OL,15,Fadded: "Given the scale and immediacy
OL,16,Fof this crisis, we have asked the
OL,17,FPrime Minister to act decisively and
OL,18,Fwithout delay."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]wD@HOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
