OL,3,CNI political leader write to Starmer
OL,4,Crequesting action against fuel costs
OL,6,FThe trade union Nipsa said the fuel
OL,7,Fcrisis is placing "intense pressure"
OL,8,Fon workers.
OL,10,FThe union said fuel prices in Northern
OL,11,FIreland have risen faster than
OL,12,Fanywhere else in the UK.
OL,14,FDeputy general secretary Patrick
OL,15,FMulholland said: "The fuel crisis is
OL,16,Fadding significant pressure to the
OL,17,Fcostofliving emergency, particularly
OL,18,Ffor workers who have no practical
OL,19,Falternative but to travel by car.
OL,26,@oD@SOUoD@dO]wD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
