PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775927152
OL,3,CNI political leader write to Starmer
OL,4,Crequesting action against fuel costs
OL,6,F"These unprecedented price rises are
OL,7,Fpushing household budgets to breaking
OL,8,Fpoint and creating real anxiety about
OL,9,Fsimply getting to work."
OL,11,FLarge parts of the Republic of Ireland
OL,12,Fhave seen widespread disruption in
OL,13,Frecent days due to protests about the
OL,14,Fspiralling cost of fuel.
OL,16,FPosts on social media have indicated
OL,17,Fthat similar protests are scheduled
OL,18,Ffor locations in Northern Ireland in
OL,19,Fcoming days.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
