OL,3,CNI political leader write to Starmer
OL,4,Crequesting action against fuel costs
OL,6,FThis comes as hundreds of petrol
OL,7,Fstations in the Republic of Ireland
OL,8,Fare without fuel, with a warning that
OL,9,Fas many as 500 could be empty by this
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,12,FIt's after a series of protests and
OL,13,Fblockades over the last 4 days over
OL,14,Fthe rising cost of fuel.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
