CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775927152
OL,3,CNI political leader write to Starmer
OL,4,Crequesting action against fuel costs
OL,6,FThe protesters have been engaging with
OL,7,Fgovernment ministers in Dublin this
OL,8,Fafternoon saying they will continue to
OL,9,Fprotests until they get a result, but
OL,10,Fthe Taoiseach has warned ships
OL,11,Fcarrying oil could have to be turned
OL,12,Faway from ports due to blockages at an
OL,13,Foil refinery.
OL,15,FThe protesters have a "number of mixed
OL,16,Fmessages", the president of the Irish
OL,17,FRoad Haulage Association has said.
OL,26,@wD@WOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
