PN,44612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775927152
OL,3,CNI political leader write to Starmer
OL,4,Crequesting action against fuel costs
OL,6,FHeading into a meeting with the
OL,7,FGovernment at the Department of
OL,8,FAgriculture on Friday afternoon Ger
OL,9,FHyland was asked what messages the
OL,10,Fprotesters had requested he deliver.
OL,12,FHe said: "There's a number of mixed
OL,13,Fmessages. They have their asks going
OL,14,Finto the meeting and it'll be
OL,15,Fdiscussed inside in the meeting. I'm
OL,16,Fnot going to pre-empt anything."
OL,26,@tD@JOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775927152
OL,3,CNI political leader write to Starmer
OL,4,Crequesting action against fuel costs
OL,6,FHe added: "I hope by this evening, we
OL,7,Fmight have some sort of a resolution,
OL,8,For an end, or something that maybe can
OL,9,Ftake these people off the streets and
OL,10,Fthe roads."
OL,12,FHe said he felt "apprehensive", adding
OL,13,Fthere is "a lot riding on this
OL,14,Fmeeting".
OL,16,F"The stakes are massive for both the
OL,17,Fcountry, ourselves, for the people
OL,18,Fthat's on the protest," he added.
